OL,3,CRent caps, no 'revenge evictions' and
OL,4,Cnew tribunal proposed by Housing
OL,5,CMinister
OL,7,FJersey's Housing Minister has lodged
OL,8,Fhis plans to dramatically change
OL,9,FJersey's tenancy laws.
OL,11,FAfter previously revealing some
OL,12,Fdetail, the full amendment to the law
OL,13,Fhas now been revealed and Deputy Sam
OL,14,FMezec says it will help "alleviate the
OL,15,Fhousing crises" in the island.
OL,17,FHe added: "The current law pretty much
OL,18,Fdoesn't have any limits on what
OL,19,Flandlords can do with rent increases.
