OL,3,CRent caps, no 'revenge evictions' and
OL,4,Cnew tribunal proposed by Housing
OL,5,CMinister
OL,7,F"The people who should worry are bad
OL,8,Flandlords.
OL,10,F"I expect they'll be a noisy minority
OL,11,Fwho will be worried about this - and
OL,12,Fthey should be, because my aim is to
OL,13,Fstop what they are doing."
OL,15,FThe UK's Labour government has been
OL,16,Fworking on a Renter's Right Bill - the
OL,17,FMinister described his own amendment
OL,18,Fas "Jersey's equivalent".
OL,20,FSome of the main changes include:
