OL,3,CRent caps, no 'revenge evictions' and
OL,4,Cnew tribunal proposed by Housing
OL,5,CMinister
OL,7,FThere are exemptions for rent
OL,8,Fincreases that apply for landlord-
OL,9,Femployers and social housing providers
OL,10,F- and if rent is significantly behind
OL,11,Fthe market rate, or if the property is
OL,12,Fimproved to the tenant's benefit.
OL,14,FDeputy Mezec says his plans would
OL,15,Fprovide "a clearer and fairer
OL,16,Fframework, for both landlords and
OL,17,Ftenants, on how to end a tenancy -
OL,18,Frather than the free for all that we
OL,19,Fcurrently have which can lead to
OL,20,Finjustices."
