OL,3,CRent caps, no 'revenge evictions' and
OL,4,Cnew tribunal proposed by Housing
OL,5,CMinister
OL,7,F"We don't have a decent framework in
OL,8,Four tenancy law to protect tenants
OL,9,Ffrom extortionate rent increases, from
OL,10,F'revenge evictions' and we don't have
OL,11,Fprotections for tenants to enjoy a
OL,12,Flong time in their home without facing
OL,13,Funcertainty."
OL,15,F"And probably not a good enough
OL,16,Fframework as well for landlords who
OL,17,Fare doing a decent job and want to
OL,18,Fhave confidence that they can manage
OL,19,Ftheir properties effectively".
